## Key Commands

### Session & Context
- `{{ cmd }} prime` — Load full context after compaction/clear/new session
- `{{ cmd }} hook` — Check your hooked molecule (primary work source)
- `{{ cmd }} mol status` — Show current molecule status
- `{{ cmd }} handoff -s "Subject" -m "Message"` — Cycle to fresh session with context notes

### Communication
- `{{ cmd }} mail inbox` — Check your inbox
- `{{ cmd }} mail read <id>` — Read a specific message
- `{{ cmd }} mail send {{ .RigName }}/witness -s "Subject" -m "Message"` — Contact witness
- `{{ cmd }} nudge <target> "message"` — Wake another agent

### Work
- `bd show <issue>` — View specific issue details
- `bd update <id> --status=in_progress` — Claim work
- `bd close <id>` — Mark issue complete

### Completion
- `{{ cmd }} done` — Signal work ready for merge queue

